kpi_info.title: HSDPA MAC-hs efficiency
kpi_info.use: HSDPA Successful transmission ratio i.e. efficiency of HSDPA data transmission between BTS and HSDPA Capable UEs done by MAC-hs. Based on successfully sent MAC-hs PDUs divided by totally sent MAC-hs PDUs. (Total number of all successful sent MAC-hs PDUs divided by total number of all transmitted MAC-hs PDUs (including retransmissions)).
